<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:38:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>癌症药物蛋白靶标也可能有助于对抗流感</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cancer-drug-protein-target-may-also-help-fight-influenza</link><description>根据杰克逊实验室 (JAX) 的最新研究，一种已被 FDA 批准的癌症药物靶向的蛋白质也可能有助于人体对抗流感。发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cancer-drug-protein-target-may-also-help-fight-influenza3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:38:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cancer-drug-protein-target-may-also-help-fight-influenza</guid></item><item><title>人类视觉：我们实际看到和没有看到的东西告诉我们很多关于意识的信息</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/human-vision-what-we-actually-see-and-dont-see-tells-us-a-lot-about-consciousness</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/human-vision-what-we-actually-see-and-dont-see-tells-us-a-lot-about-consciousness</guid></item><item><title>一家成立于 2025 年 4 月的西班牙初创公司以创纪录的时间验证了具有传感器融合功能的人工智能周边监控系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-spanish-startup-founded-in-april-2025-validates-in-record-time-an-ai-powered-perimeter-surveillance-system-with-sensor-fusion</link><description>西班牙初创公司 Sentitech 测试了人工智能双圆顶安全系统，该系统可在真实空中交通中跟踪长达 3 公里的威胁。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-spanish-startup-founded-in-april-2025-validates-in-record-time-an-ai-powered-perimeter-surveillance-system-with-sensor-fusion.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-spanish-startup-founded-in-april-2025-validates-in-record-time-an-ai-powered-perimeter-surveillance-system-with-sensor-fusion</guid></item><item><title>“处于我们认为可能的边缘”：天文学家在古代宇宙中发现了极其罕见的恒星</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/at-the-edge-of-what-we-thought-possible-astronomers-find-extremely-rare-star-from-ancient-universe</link><description>像这样的发现是宇宙考古学，发现了保存了宇宙第一批恒星指纹的稀有恒星化石。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/at-the-edge-of-what-we-thought-possible-astronomers-find-extremely-rare-star-from-ancient-universe.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 11:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/at-the-edge-of-what-we-thought-possible-astronomers-find-extremely-rare-star-from-ancient-universe</guid></item><item><title>陶哲轩宣布第一届SAIR比赛</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/terence-tao-announces-the-1st-sair-competition</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 11:38:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/terence-tao-announces-the-1st-sair-competition</guid></item><item><title>联合治疗对已扩散至大脑的晚期乳腺癌患者有益</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/combination-treatment-benefits-patients-with-advanced-breast-cancer-that-has-spread-to-the-brain</link><description>软脑膜转移（LM）患者历史上几乎没有治疗选择。现在，德克萨斯大学MD安德森癌症中心的研究人员发现，靶向治疗图卡替尼和曲妥珠单抗加上化疗药物卡培他滨的组合可以改善一些患有LM的乳腺癌患者的症状并延长生存期。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/combination-treatment-benefits-patients-with-advanced-breast-cancer-that-has-spread-to-the-brain.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 11:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/combination-treatment-benefits-patients-with-advanced-breast-cancer-that-has-spread-to-the-brain</guid></item><item><title>肾小球基底膜结构完整性决定层粘连蛋白在肾脏中的跨组织沉积</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/glomerular-basement-membrane-structural-integrity-dictates-trans-tissue-deposition-of-laminin-in-the-kidney</link><description>大町和林等人。揭示了阿尔波特综合征肾小球基底膜异位层粘连蛋白-α2 沉积的一个意想不到的来源。他们表明，层粘连蛋白-α2 在血液中循环并根据基底膜完整性沉积，揭示了哺乳动物细胞外基质沉积的跨组织途径。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/glomerular-basement-membrane-structural-integrity-dictates-trans-tissue-deposition-of-laminin-in-the-kidney2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 11:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/glomerular-basement-membrane-structural-integrity-dictates-trans-tissue-deposition-of-laminin-in-the-kidney</guid></item><item><title>SoulMate LLM加速器根据用户的具体特征而演变</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/soulmate-llm-accelerator-evolves-according-to-the-specific-characteristics-of-the-user</link><description>虽然像 ChatGPT 这样的大型语言模型 (LLM) 擅长回答无数问题，但它们通常仍然不知道用户的小习惯或之前的对话上下文。这就是为什么人工智能尽管已经深深融入我们的日常生活，但仍然让人感觉像个“陌生人”。韩国科学技术院的研究人员克服了这些限制，在人工智能半导体研究生院的 Hoi-Jun Yoo 教授的带领下，开发出了世界上第一个人工智能半导体，称为“SoulMate”，它可以实时学习并适应用户的言语风格、偏好和情感，成为真正的“数字灵魂伴侣”。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/soulmate-llm-accelerator-evolves-according-to-the-specific-characteristics-of-the-user.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 10:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/soulmate-llm-accelerator-evolves-according-to-the-specific-characteristics-of-the-user</guid></item><item><title>新型 ALS 相关 KIF5A 变体 c.2993-6C 的后果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/consequences-of-the-novel-als-associated-kif5a-variant-c-2993-6c</link><description>UvrD 家族 DNA 解旋酶/转位酶的调节和激活。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/consequences-of-the-novel-als-associated-kif5a-variant-c-2993-6c2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 10:38:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/consequences-of-the-novel-als-associated-kif5a-variant-c-2993-6c</guid></item><item><title>新的绘图技术区分健康衰老与阿尔茨海默病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-mapping-technique-distinguishes-healthy-aging-from-alzheimers</link><description>研究人员开发了一种高分辨率空间蛋白质组学方法来绘制大脑中蛋白质和糖的变化。该研究确定了区分健康衰老与阿尔茨海默病和路易体病的分子特征。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-mapping-technique-distinguishes-healthy-aging-from-alzheimers.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 10:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-mapping-technique-distinguishes-healthy-aging-from-alzheimers</guid></item></channel></rss>